welcome_message_body: Welcome to Sun Prairie! A charming city known for its beautiful parks, friendly community, and delicious local restaurants. We invite you to explore and experience all that Sun Prairie has to offer. Enjoy your stay!

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Dane County Regional Airport serves all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Concourse A
terminals.description: Concourse A at Dane County Regional Airport serves primarily domestic flights and is home to various airlines.

terminals.name: Concourse B
terminals.description: Concourse B at Dane County Regional Airport serves primarily international flights and is home to various airlines.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
